{"tid":146600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東區醫院18歲男病人被44歲院友摸下體","createTime":"2017-03-07T08:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T01:23:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"149b2175a17c37ee75608ed4b3ce4b83aacfa257","tid":146600,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"東區醫院又爆出男病人遭院友非禮的風化案件。今晨7時，警方接獲醫院職員報案，指院內一名18歲男病人，疑被44歲男院友非禮，警員接報到場，經初步調查後，拘捕該名44歲男院友，案件交由東區警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進，消息稱發生今次非禮案的也是精神科病房，連本案在內，今次已是一個多月內爆出第4名公院男病人遭侵犯事件。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，18歲男事主患有思覺失調，44歲被捕院友則患精神分裂，兩人入住同一精神科病房一段時間。今晨6時，受害人睡夢中發現該名院友摸其下體，其後告知醫護人員，人員報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n上月13日，留醫東區醫院的17歲精神科男病人會見醫生時透露．遭一名年長的男院友非禮包括摸下體，醫護人員報警，警方拘捕69歲男院友。本報正向東區醫院查詢。"},{"pid":"ca21c0a06e44b594deb2d97e6de55df213a3bf63","tid":146600,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170307&amp;guid=56396371&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170307%26guid%3D56396371%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=kDoZHsh44GLEl9RERzeBg0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e3b951da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170307%26guid%3D56396371%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=7ed0f063\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170307&amp;guid=56396371&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"d25163a6baebc2afdc4ec95802952051ff8acf3d","tid":146600,"uid":968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b5b24061d9f8470e58aba9fc5f7f3e25f430dd","tid":146600,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":